learning_outcomes.en:
Upon successful completion of the course, students should be able to:
- evaluate and criticize research designs/empirical research produced by others;
- read and understand scholarly articles that employ commonly used quantitative methods;
- understand basic descriptive and inferential statistics and use R software; 
- understand that science needs more quantitative detail than the directional model "when x goes up, y goes down";
- understand that our theoretical and empirical equations must not predict absurdities;
- graph the entire conceptually allowed field, view data within this logical framework.

learning_outcomes.et:
Kursuse läbinu:
- teab peamisi sotsiaalteaduste kvantitatiivseid meetodeid ja analüüsitehnikaid;
- oskab seletada erinevate meetodite plusse ja miinuseid ning rakendusvõimalusi;
- oskab valida uurimisküsimusele ja andmestikule vastava meetodi;
- oskab hinnata teiste teadustööd metodoloogilisest vaatepunktist.
